column5: Where is everyong going for the opener?
What's the location of Pipestone lake ???
North of Emo to Clearwater (Burditt) Lake. North end of Clearwater to Mechanical portage and into the south end of Pipestone.
Good choice....where do you stay I was raised there.
Stay at Gateway North Outfitters outpost cabin located in Watson Bay. We do really well close to the cabin and in the NW Arm as well.
We are going to Lower Manitou lake for opener, stay at Camp Manitou in the stretch. This will be the first time for us. It should be great. Mark1
Fishful Thinker Have you considered Cliff Lake, 32 miles north of Vermilion Bay?
